OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry but rather cloudy evening.
OL,7,FOvernight, conditions will stay dry
OL,8,Ffor most areas, though a few isolated
OL,9,Fshowers may develop later in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,12,Fday with patchy cloud. A few showers
OL,13,Fmay develop from late morning, these
OL,14,Fmostly light and clearing away through
OL,15,Fthe afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,18,Fand settled throughout this period
OL,19,Fwith a good deal of sunshine. Light
OL,20,Fwinds at first but becoming breezier
OL,21,Fby Thursday on eastern coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
